{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, the library was digested with USER (0.0625U/ul, M5505L) in 1x NEBuffer DpnII in parallel reactions (about 2.5ug each) for 6 h at 37 °C followed by 3 h at room temperature and purified with Zymo ssDNA/RNA clean & concentrator kit.",
    "The overall workflow, including reverse transcription, cDNA crosslinking, padlock probe capture, RCA, rolony crosslinking and image acquisition, is illustrated in Fig. 1.",
    "A step-by-step protocol can be found at protocols.io (dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.e6nvwjxnzlmk/v1).",
    "Reverse transcription and cDNA crosslinking.",
    "Tissue sections were fixed in 4% PFA in 1x PBS at 4 °C for 1 h, followed by two 3-minute washes with PBST (1x PBS and 0.1% Tween-20)."
  ]
}